    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional caliber. This unit is in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface, from the hand-polished exterior to the immaculate cabin, remains in factory-fresh state. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical perfection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
