    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It's in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
