    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the E46 M3, featuring the naturally aspirated S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing. This vehicle is in concours-level condition, showcasing flawless factory paint and an interior free of typical bolster wear or trim delamination. Mechanically, it is turn-key: the rod bearing service is documented, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum expansion tank and high-flow water pump. The Getrag six-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate entry, paired with a refreshed M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains factory-spec compliance, ensuring the razor-sharp turn-in and telepathic feedback this chassis is known for. A meticulously maintained, investment-grade icon for the serious purist.",
